## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some articles may not reflect the most current statistics or consider all possible factors influencing the gender pay gap. Additionally, the focus was primarily on the United States, which may not fully represent global trends. Further research could include a broader range of international perspectives and more recent data to provide a comprehensive view.